dc_description_s: This polygon layer represents building footprints for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabse Calumet_Buildings_2017.gdb
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://gis-calumet.hub.arcgis.com/. This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
